  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your smoker to 120°C.",
    "Season the beef shin with salt and black pepper.",
    "Place the beef shin in the smoker and smoke for 2 hours.",
    "Meanwhile, peel and grate the yuca and set aside.",
    "Heat the coconut oil in a pan over medium heat and sauté the garlic until fragrant.",
    "Add the grated yuca to the pan and cook until crispy.",
    "Mix the pimenta cheese, farofa and cilantro in a bowl.",
    "After the beef is smoked, let it rest for 30 minutes before slicing.",
    "Serve the beef with the crispy yuca, pimenta cheese mixture and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Garnish with cilantro and serve immediately."
  ],
